data.title: Portland Senior Photos
data.text:
Collection One

$549

Lifestyle SESSION

We’ll shoot for up to 1.5 to 2 hours at 2 nearby locations within 20 miles of Downtown Portland. This is the perfect amount of time to capture plenty of candid moments and portraits. Sessions can include one outfit change, props or pets, and some portraits in a cap and gown.

HELP ALONG THE WAY

Receive unlimited planning and consultation for your session. I’ll lend a hand in recommending locations, provide feedback on outfit and footwear choices, work with you on prop ideas, or whatever else helps to make your session feel easy and stress free.

YOUR PHOTOS

You will receive all of the final edited high resolution digital files with unlimited downloads, sharing, and personal printing rights. Your photos will be delivered via a fast and easy to use online gallery that allows for sharing on social media. It’s also connected to a professional print lab.

Collection Two

$400

yEARBOOK HIGHLIGHT

We’ll shoot for 30 to 45 minutes at 1 location within 20 miles of Downtown Portland. This is enough time to capture that photo for the yearbook as well as some candid moments.

HELP ALONG THE WAY

Receive unlimited planning and consultation for your session. I’ll lend a hand in recommending locations, provide feedback on outfit and footwear choices, or whatever else helps to make your session feel easy and stress free.

YOUR PHOTOS

You will receive all of the final edited high resolution for viewing and proofing and can select 10 photos to download. Additional photos will be available for purchase and for printing. Your photos will be delivered via a fast and easy to use online gallery that allows for sharing on social media. It’s also connected to a professional print lab.
